comments: It's hard because Ayala is leaving. The course with her was just phenomenal and I'd recommend it to anyone. I hope the department can keep up that standard!
Great continuation in the Hebrew sequence.
I would definitely recommend Hebrew to someone who is interested in a less work-intense but more intellectually satisfying language!
